{"tid":2192310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜糖護蘋 出位廣告熱爆","createTime":"2020-09-07T04:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T02:54:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"83d18c2d0ad0bf99a73c7e552bc31490da88316f","tid":2192310,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:47:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/HJBZYEM4AJGMXBYWMO7HDDQ4IA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FHJBZYEM4AJGMXBYWMO7HDDQ4IA%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=0e4cabba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FHJBZYEM4AJGMXBYWMO7HDDQ4IA%2F&h=bd0eef81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/HJBZYEM4AJGMXBYWMO7HDDQ4IA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n姜糖護蘋 出位廣告熱爆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JMyOd_DV-2oAIbwPmJQV1a1jYko=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UXQPG44MIFBFTDTFGD5COVL3UA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJMyOd_DV-2oAIbwPmJQV1a1jYko%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUXQPG44MIFBFTDTFGD5COVL3UA.jpg&h=b203b1be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■F小姐會購買姜濤代言產品，對歌迷會紀念品更珍而重之。<br />\n<br />\n8月11日起，大家突然多了個看報紙廣告的習慣，歌迷F小姐（化名）則多了個落廣告的習慣。她在《蘋果》一連十日落了一則分類小廣告，寫上「姜濤不紅，天理不容」，八粒細字擲地有聲，成為網民熱話。有電台DJ都在節目中討論，連登討論區的巴絲都好奇誰是姜濤？後來F小姐再追加九日附有QR Code的分類小廣告，說要在疫潮之下以姜濤的新歌《蒙着嘴說愛你》為港人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n「其實最初好簡單，我一心想登廣告撐《蘋果》，但我又唔係公司冇product要sell，想輕鬆啲冇咁政治化，就落無厘頭句子，我。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n姜濤2018年參與Viutv的《全民造星》比賽勝出出道，憑其甜美笑容收服不少媽媽級fans，以往其粉絲都會自稱「姜糖」，而「姜濤不紅，天理不容」並非F小姐自創，而是fans圈內流傳已久的金句，作者已不可考。<br />\n<br />\nF小姐細說迷上姜濤有千萬個理由，豈止外形、歌聲與舞技，「佢由《全民造星》出道，我哋好似睇住佢大咁，見證佢真係好努力，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WAtz-Y3oncS0PDDCso7cr3iBkPo=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZZESYG6OXBAAZCQGYYZ4EZF6XI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWAtz-Y3oncS0PDDCso7cr3iBkPo%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZZESYG6OXBAAZCQGYYZ4EZF6XI.jpg&h=0891354c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■F小姐刊登了附有QR Code的分類小廣告，讀者可憑此連結至姜濤新歌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n追星助走出情緒谷底<br />\n<br />\nF小姐笑說自己年輕時迷黎明也沒這樣瘋狂，幸好丈夫和家人都很支持她追星，只是起初兒子不太習慣，媽媽迷上一個跟自己差不多的明星，但這次分類小廣告的QR Code都是阿仔負責。首十日花了900元製作的分類小廣告帶來的討論，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「估唔到咁大迴響，原來有好多人未聽過姜濤，睇YouTube留言先知好多人因為呢個小廣告而去睇佢個MV，我都好開心！」F小姐解。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nF小姐笑說自己行為上算不上最瘋狂的粉絲，「我未試過去排通頂，未試過追星追。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Vy9ZoK4jwctZWlQC9l8xv7ZoTdQ=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X3ICGL3LDZFRTALHQFPSEHW5VA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVy9ZoK4jwctZWlQC9l8xv7ZoTdQ%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX3ICGL3LDZFRTALHQFPSEHW5VA.jpg&h=1e89254d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「姜濤不紅，天理不容」分類小廣告引起網民無限想像，背後推手是忠實「姜糖」F小姐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PZGpL0tUBBRK47MIKiwxUPBMne0=/1252x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AA74PXO6A5BWJBBHQVMYJNX7A4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPZGpL0tUBBRK47MIKiwxUPBMne0%3D%2F1252x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAA74PXO6A5BWJBBHQVMYJNX7A4.jpg&h=b9617c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■除了F小姐所落的姜濤廣告外，其他小廣告亦甚具創意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣告變市民宣洩平台<br />\n<br />\nF小姐回想自己在《蘋果》創刊已是讀者，一看廿多年到近年全家都網上訂閱，成為VIP訂戶，但已有近十年沒有購買實體報紙，因為搜報館事件重新買報，「見到黎生被人拉，又見到搜報館，睇到好心痛、好唔開心，其實我同細佬妹都已經訂晒《蘋果》同《壹週刊》，咁仲可以做啲咩呢？咁就諗到不如落廣告啦」。<br />\n<br />\n她說以往實體報紙廣告與自己沒有關係，看見都只會想翻走，但國安法之下，言論空間收窄，廣告變成香港人自由表達的平台，宣洩內心不滿，「可能有啲嘢唔敢講，變咗要喺廣告曲線咁表達」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n她亦感受到報紙廣告的威力，在她的分類小廣告出現的第十日，姜濤在其IG Story將廣告貼堂，還留言寫上「不為別的，只為了謝謝這一位很有心的歌迷」。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a75c9ea9a851c1ed89037820d3ca973d7047565f","tid":2192310,"uid":40272,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRH4eZx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRH4eZx.png&h=183b317f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eea0fda103b25cbf39e66f01f15e2a055bf82b2","tid":2192310,"uid":196446,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"收皮啦樓主兜咁大個圈又想屈姜濤係藍絲<br />\n藍絲會唔會自己出首歌寫<strong><span class=\"red\">不撒不退</span></strong>呀？<br />\n就算唔係黃都一定唔係藍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一次錯手like就想抹煞人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8710b4e560b08f03255062288b75d8ff1ec0c0","tid":2192310,"uid":127575,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">我唔明白姜濤有咩魅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c96b95b830d5d9f67a3b38a30cb81a13d270caf2","tid":2192310,"uid":246787,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"鼓勵同靠班中女fans出錢賣廣告 真係好垃圾"},{"pid":"086c5fecfacf70d4000afe1cd7ac0ec4fb54d21e","tid":2192310,"uid":227597,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c96b95b830d5d9f67a3b38a30cb81a13d270caf2","tid":2192310,"uid":246787,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"鼓勵同靠班中女fans出錢賣廣告 真係好垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:14:54.000Z","msg":"證據呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi